dct_title_s: Exeter street plan with index showing all bus routes, service frequencies, and other information.
dct_description_sm: Exeter Publicity and Information Bureau. City of Exeter Transport Department. Alternate title: Street plan of Exeter. Based on the Ordnance Survey map with the sanction of the Controller of H. M. Stationery Office. With street index. Verso: title panel and advertisement.
